--------------- Exercises
> Huong dich:
>   Gia su da co output trang thai thu n-1
>   Tim output trang thai thu n

> sample code:
def enumerate(i): # i 
    if i == n-1:
        p(S)
    else:
        for j in D:
            S[i] = j
            enumerate(i+1)


1. Liet ke cac chuoi nhi phan co do dai n.
Thuat toan:
Gia su, ta da co chuoi nhi phan s co do dai i.
Them 0 hoac 1 vao cuoi s, ta co chuoi nhi phan do dai i+1.

Code: ex01.py
                    .....
                    
                    
2. Cho tap A gom n phan tu, ex: A = {1,7,3,10}
Tim tat ca tap con B sao cho, sum(B) = t, t cho truoc.
Thuat toan:
Bai toan co hai:
    - Tim cac tap con B cua tap A
    - Kiem tra sum(B) == t

De co mot tap con B cua tap A.
Ta tim mot chuoi nhi phan s co do dai n.
Neu s[i] == 1, thi A[i] duoc chon vao tap con B.
Neu s[i] == 0, thi A[i] khong duoc chon.
De tim chuoi nhi phan s, ta su dung lai cach lam cua bai 1.

De kiem tra sum(B) == t,
ta tinh tong cua cac phan tu A[i] vua duoc chon
roi so sanh voi t.

Code: ex02.py
                    .....
                    
                    
3. Cho tap A gom cac loai mat hang nhu, ex: A {coc, xoai, oi, cam}
Chon 2 mat hang tu tap A, liet ke tat ca cach chon
Thuat toan:
Gia su, ta da chon duoc k mat hang va cho vao gio B.
De co k+1 mat hang,
ta lay mot mat hang chua duoc chon va cho no vao gio B.

Code: ex03.py

